    "id": "medicaid-colorado-rules-2024",
    "name": "Colorado Medicaid Eligibility Rules (2024)",
    "description": "Colorado-specific Medicaid eligibility rules for 2024. Colorado HAS expanded Medicaid under the ACA, providing coverage to adults with income up to 138% of the Federal Poverty Level. These rules reflect Colorado's Medicaid program (Health First Colorado).",
